message.content: Sama da cikakken tarihin sata ta hanyar sata bayanan sirri na wasu. Sata ta hanyar sata bayanan sirri na wasu shine bayanin da za'a iya samun bayani game da cikakken matukar sata, bayanin da za'a iya yin shirin sata, bayanin da za'a iya samun bayani game da damuwa, da dai sauransu. Don Allah, a kira ni domin ko wane bayanin da za'a iya samun.
